content: Ah, the buzz of NYC. Back in my element. First thing? Bought a huge coffee from my favorite spot on 5th Ave.
Just turned 22, and it's time to level up. Spent the morning sketching out ideas for a quantum-resistant blockchain framework. The city's energy is fueling my ambition.
Had a breakthrough with my Rust learning—finally got a handle on ownership and borrowing. Feels like I'm unlocking a new level of programming wizardry.
